                        .time
                            | Expected response time: 
                            span 72 hours
                        a.doc_border_btn.doc_border_btn_two(href='mailto:ycyclasscom@gmail.com') Email Us
                .row.get_info_item.align-items-center.justify-content-between
                    .col-lg-4.col-sm-5
                        .media
                            img(src='img/twitter.png' alt='')
                            .media-body
                                h5.h5.bold Twitter
                                p Monday to Friday
                    .col-lg-8.col-sm-7.d-flex.align-items-center.justify-content-between
                        .time
